    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A survival horror game, where an island engulfs its visitors, including you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features and mechanics:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a multi-level world with a changing environment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight strange entities, along with a range of enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage your inventory and resources.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine items and purchase items.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Acquire an assortment of weapons.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat bosses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve puzzles.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shortly after the death of your father, you decide to find your long-lost brother. You take the old fishing boat and cast your fate into the sea.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256840/extras/aa4dd7e2ec65b5d4b848421f5e8ae7b9.poster.avif?t=1754658019\" width=600 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256840/extras/aa4dd7e2ec65b5d4b848421f5e8ae7b9.webm?t=1754658019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256840/extras/aa4dd7e2ec65b5d4b848421f5e8ae7b9.mp4?t=1754658019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Along your way, you will encounter many hostile and passive creatures. However, they all seem to know more than you do, keeping you in the mist, almost as if they want you to be confused and lost.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256840/extras/8adda61a33652187f2637d601141656d.poster.avif?t=1754658019\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256840/extras/8adda61a33652187f2637d601141656d.webm?t=1754658019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256840/extras/8adda61a33652187f2637d601141656d.mp4?t=1754658019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This mysterious journey eventually turns into a fearful trip through hellish environments.</p>",
